{"tid":2284844,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"城大女生急性肝衰竭陷昏迷　急需 A- 或 O- 型血肝移植　親友：或未能渡過本周末","createTime":"2020-11-13T15:25:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-13T16:40:06.000Z","uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"851c0fde6032ac832f4557a870fe74e387a74d95","tid":2284844,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T15:25:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/posts/3634944343257826\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fposts%2F3634944343257826&d=28xXuG3%2BZgR4L17YEenOIh0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=e91bbadf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/posts/3634944343257826</a><br />\n<br />\n20 歲城市大學化學系學生、保良局李城璧中學校友鄭如妍本月初患上急性肝衰竭，現正留醫瑪麗醫院深切治療部，急需換肝續命。其親友今（ 11 日）發文呼籲有心人士捐肝，好友邱小姐向《立場新聞》透露，如妍上月起持續發燒未退，服藥治療後出現急性肝衰竭，其後變得神智不清，更陷入昏迷。<br />\n<br />\n若本周仍沒有合適人士捐肝，如妍或未能渡過今個周末。邱小姐形容如妍為人活潑、孝順，一直希望盡快大學畢業，賺錢供養母親。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/城大女生急性肝衰竭陷昏迷-急需-a-或-o-型血肝移植-親友-或未能渡過本周末/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E5%9F%8E%E5%A4%A7%E5%A5%B3%E7%94%9F%E6%80%A5%E6%80%A7%E8%82%9D%E8%A1%B0%E7%AB%AD%E9%99%B7%E6%98%8F%E8%BF%B7-%E6%80%A5%E9%9C%80-a-%E6%88%96-o-%E5%9E%8B%E8%A1%80%E8%82%9D%E7%A7%BB%E6%A4%8D-%E8%A6%AA%E5%8F%8B-%E6%88%96%E6%9C%AA%E8%83%BD%E6%B8%A1%E9%81%8E%E6%9C%AC%E5%91%A8%E6%9C%AB%2F&d=28xXuG3%2BZgR4L17YEenOIh0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=dd0226ca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E5%9F%8E%E5%A4%A7%E5%A5%B3%E7%94%9F%E6%80%A5%E6%80%A7%E8%82%9D%E8%A1%B0%E7%AB%AD%E9%99%B7%E6%98%8F%E8%BF%B7-%E6%80%A5%E9%9C%80-a-%E6%88%96-o-%E5%9E%8B%E8%A1%80%E8%82%9D%E7%A7%BB%E6%A4%8D-%E8%A6%AA%E5%8F%8B-%E6%88%96%E6%9C%AA%E8%83%BD%E6%B8%A1%E9%81%8E%E6%9C%AC%E5%91%A8%E6%9C%AB%2F&h=7e1d4f15\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/城大女生急性肝衰竭陷昏迷-急需-a-或-o-型血肝移植-親友-或未能渡過本周末/</a>"},{"pid":"e9afa3e0beb8